<paragraph blockId="12.[151,756,1956,2077]" pageId="12" pageNumber="87">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,284,1956,1979]" pageId="12" pageNumber="87">Comments:</emphasis>
This species is a member of the 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Lobl" baseAuthorityYear="1971" box="[668,756,1956,1979]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Baeocera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="87" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lenta">
